|-
| {{tl2|Harvard citation text}} || {{tl2|harvtxt}} || {{harvtxt|Smith|2006|p=25}}
|-
| {{tl2|Harvard citation with colon text}} || {{tl2|harvcoltxt}} || {{Harvcoltxt|Smith|2006|p=25}}
|-
