** {{harvc|last1=Stout|first1=P. R.|last2=Johnson|first2=C. M.|year=1957|c=Trace Elements |url=https://archive.org/stream/yoa1957#page/n167/mode/1up |in=Stefferud |ignore-err=yes}}
